"The shape of the returned matrix is ``x.shape + (order,)``, where :math:"
"`order = (deg[0]+1)*(deg([1]+1)*(deg[2]+1)`.  The dtype will be the same as "
"the converted `x`, `y`, and `z`."
msgstr ""

